Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:06.86,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:33.72,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun \Narrived at the Witches' Forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.36,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,searching for a magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.49,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to take advantage of \Nthe chaos they were causing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:41.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Diamond Kingdom came to steal \Nthe Queen of Witches' secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:43.16,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Million Lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:48.04,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll just have to kill this chick first!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.54,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:56.72,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Your lessons got through to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.61,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fanzell's former student Mars, who was \Nstill in the Diamond Kingdom's army,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:02.72,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,decided he would side with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:04.43,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you protecting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:08.04,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,As Ladros said, we're traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:10.31,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,And you lost your memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:13.78,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm on your side, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.83,0:01:17.45,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Deflect it over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, but okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:29.17,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,By taking advantage of Asta's anti-magic, \Nthey successfully defeated Ladros.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:33.92,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment they tried to finish off Fana\Nof the Eye of the Midnight Sun's Third Eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:36.09,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,who was weakened by Noelle's spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:38.09,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.22,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:41.18,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.55,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,My student Fana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fana, who had lost her memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:48.14,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,fell into a deeper state of confusion \Nand tried to self-destruct, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:51.15,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Everything should just... disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:55.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Mars risked their lives to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:03.66,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see the world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:07.79,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:11.25,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise, Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:20.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fana regained her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:32.85,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}Those Who Boost Each Other Up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.10,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.03,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.20,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have done it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.21,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:07.66,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason for the weak \Nto stand on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.51,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I was born to break people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.83,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.12,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:19.63,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The weak will perish,\N and only the strong will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:26.01,flashback,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as naïve as you \Ncannot win against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:29.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That was all your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:33.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you were able to \Nsave your childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:36.32,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Is he your friend, Mars?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:41.52,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So you made a friend \Nin the outside world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.53,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn't say he's—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:48.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's totally my friend! \NWe did fight once, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.28,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you calmed down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But what the heck happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:06.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid dummy! Why do you have to do \Nsuch drastic things every single time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.68,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Were you born just to try to kill yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.80,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You barely have any clothes on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:14.98,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,You're a magnificent student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.19,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.23,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Master Fanzell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:24.94,flashback,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Your powers exist to protect others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.32,flashback,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.35,flashback,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:36.29,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're both alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you barely remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:44.82,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:48.09,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,After the final training, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:52.56,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly believe she's \Nstarted breathing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:58.35,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the power of the magic that bears \Nthe Phoenix's name? Or could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.43,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,How fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.06,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fit Fana with a mage stone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:07.60,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,What a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:11.59,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did it fail to increase her \Nmagic, but she hardly has any left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:14.62,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that was the last dying ember of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:18.10,flashback,Morris,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of her. She's of \Nno interest to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.22,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.27,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,My old friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.26,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as it was long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:35.55,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Humans even hurt other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.40,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, I shall destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.65,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But... I need your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.02,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You will live on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.92,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any memories after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:55.14,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,It felt as though someone \Nelse entered my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.79,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Like I was being controlled...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:02.79,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,All I remember is that \Nperson's fierce hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What about the third eye \Nand pointy ears you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.55,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry. \NI don't know anything about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.25,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You went through all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.20,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.88,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, you don't need to \Nfeel bad about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.56,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we got to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.99,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll never let you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.94,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Let's stay together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.19,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:30.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,My, my! Aren't things heating up over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:34.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He's stiffened up as hard as a \Nchunk of ore. How adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:38.54,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Childhood friends tragically torn \Napart and reunited by destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.83,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That's really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.83,0:07:43.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he's bawling over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Finral?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:49.22,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous and envious and bummed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't have any childhood friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:54.58,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't have any cute \Nchildhood friends like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:58.22,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! Nope! Nope! Not one, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:59.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of them, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.55,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I'm not jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd I just get slapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:14.49,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why did the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun come to the Witches' Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:24.04,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel a strong desire in my head \Nto retrieve the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magic stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.97,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,So that means there's a \Nmagic stone in this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and go see the Queen of Witches!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:40.16,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,No, before that, we need to save Domina, \NMariella, and the wounded witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is this ki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.77,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! His magical power should be gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.03,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:16.42,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was some intense magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:21.96,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,It took forever to absorb it all. \NThanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:24.68,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I must admit, I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:28.06,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros... But your magic \Npower should've been depleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:31.46,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I emitted it all, and then took it back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:35.90,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You rely too much on your \Nmagic detection, Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:40.64,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Really, though, why do all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:44.34,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,keep putting your own lives \Nin danger to protect others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.25,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.29,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why I'm\N gonna end up killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:10:00.48,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, some weirdo just showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:03.01,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't concern you,\Nso could you get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's got lots to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.02,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:17.74,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Why do all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:21.28,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,keep putting your own lives \Nin danger to protect others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.33,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.33,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why I'm\N gonna end up killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:37.55,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, some weirdo just showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.05,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't concern you,\Nso could you get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's got lots to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.51,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.47,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.38,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.81,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use a recovery spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.69,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cast anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:57.07,italics,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to my body? Is my magic gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:02.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on! I'm gonna pound this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:06.44,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait a sec! You're that one guy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:09.66,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,The anti-magic knight or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.20,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I totally feel your pain, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.16,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I was born without a magic attribute myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:20.92,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I was a kid, everybody made\N fun of me and called me bland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:25.13,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, you're even more worthless than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:27.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.94,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda feel bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some of your magic, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:33.75,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I would if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:36.48,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.63,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Here. All yours if you can reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:45.57,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What a great reaction! I think \Nwe'd make great partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.74,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna team up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:51.25,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You can be my right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:54.79,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to the Diamond Army for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:57.50,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rise up through the \Nroyal army's ranks together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:01.63,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,We'll teach the guys who get all cocky \Njust because they've got talent a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:07.93,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. I'm gonna make his \Nanti-magic powers all mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:10.57,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:13.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King\N of the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:18.81,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Wizard King? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:24.82,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate idiots! Million Lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:30.83,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about how you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.57,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Without that spatial magic guy over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:37.58,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,you can't do a thing about \Nlong-distance spells, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.59,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You make the perfect target!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:46.01,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That ricochet trick won't work on me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.11,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Recycle, recycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:50.91,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can win! Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:02.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And you won't get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:06.57,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.82,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:15.01,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two kinds of people\N in this world: the users and the used.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:19.45,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I won my way to the top by \Nusing the people around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.83,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use Mars over there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:26.09,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,and the girl next to him to \Nget myself even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:31.60,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll let the military use them \Nfor magic research until they die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:41.25,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You're not \Nletting me get away with this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.28,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You can be my stepping stone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:49.68,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.66,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:05.88,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not good! My magic's draining away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:09.88,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I-It won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.69,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait... You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:14.51,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,From this? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.51,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Everything I've worked for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:20.48,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! All I did was take my \Neyes off of him for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.87,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'd made it to the rank of \Nthe Eight Shining Generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:24.02,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Bad! Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.39,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:34.74,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really just throw this stupidly \Nheavy sword all the way up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.64,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of decision was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.82,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.91,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Shit! This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:47.93,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me I'm gonna be \Ntaken out by a dumbass attack like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:51.38,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Stay back! Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have made it this far on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:15:00.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,People taught me how to use \Nmy power and how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:02.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We got through life or death \Nsituations together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We helped each other out \Nwhile improving how we fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.73,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I've been able \Nto react to the attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:13.32,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,is because of something called "ki" \Nfrom back in my homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.57,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.98,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Where I come from, we've got this saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:20.33,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,"A warrior never goes back on his word."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:24.27,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were going to \Nbecome the Wizard King, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.81,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass your limits. Right here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.51,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:33.67,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:39.06,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Cradle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.81,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.14,flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.77,flashbackitalics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet everything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.69,flashbackitalics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,on this one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:53.86,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a failure anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:58.18,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:02.19,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.62,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let us help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.84,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.21,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That attack of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.59,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,will end up being incredibly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:14.59,flashback,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:24.69,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.24,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Bull Thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:36.24,flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.39,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.07,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My special move was a complete success!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:45.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Friends are only meant to be used?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not my friends! My friends and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:51.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We boost each other up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:54.85,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:59.64,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop hurting people! Please spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:03.06,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Take out this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.89,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it out on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.57,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:13.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I know how strong you are,\Nso I'm not gonna get careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:16.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I take it out and you attack me,\NI have no chance of winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I'd missed when I \Nthrew it at you, I would've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an idiot, so I can't afford \Nto mess up to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.72,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,No, please... I-I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.06,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't come out, I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:28.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough to kill anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I missed your vital points on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:34.50,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I thought I'd be able \Nto trick an idiot like him if I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.48,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,tugged at his heartstrings, \Nbut he's not buying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:37.87,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:41.49,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This twerp's been through \Nhis share of battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:45.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm gonna whack you \Nagain and knock you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:49.44,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.51,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is all of my remaining magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.44,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,If I attack him and he blocks it,\NI'm really finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:02.28,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to use reinforcement \Nmagic and force it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.16,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:09.54,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I've got enough left for two magic bullets...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:16.35,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You're Fana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.66,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.51,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you got those powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:25.10,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,but use that huge magic of yours right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:28.73,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huge magic? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:31.06,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Quit playing dumb, and hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.11,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Do it or I'll kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.56,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.57,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:40.07,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,The next shot will really kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:44.99,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:46.75,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,And there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:48.55,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:51.46,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the ultimate gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.40,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This magic's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:02.34,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like my body's gonna burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:30.66,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest magic I've ever eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:34.75,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! This power \Nsurpasses the spirit's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:37.59,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an amount a human can emit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.92,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.80,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Payback time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.93,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I tracked it with ki, but it was still \Nso fast that I couldn't dodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.61,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I've obtained the ultimate power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:02.21,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,If I use this, the other Eight Shining \NGenerals don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:05.91,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Forget them! I can take \Nover the whole kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:06.95,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:10.74,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll murder everyone who \Never looked down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:15.33,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I guess \NI'd better finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.14,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get careless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:22.63,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep hitting you with ranged \Nattacks that you can't block...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:26.51,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,until you're in pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:29.89,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.77,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,He's turned the tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:42.59,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Since he can use that sword, I thought \Nhe might be their descendant, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.55,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Show me who you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:57.39,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, how many more shots can \Nthat body you're so proud of take?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:58.46,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:50.57,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.83,0:22:49.41,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:54.07,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,How Does It Taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:53.36,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,How Does It Taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:06.71,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This is the greatest magic I've ever eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:07.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:10.98,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that tastes very regal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:12.22,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That's royalty for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:13.63,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:17.22,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. Yours tastes a little mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:18.33,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:23.08,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,This tastes really nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:23.91,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.91,0:23:25.86,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes like pickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:29.92,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that not only do I look \Nold, but my magic tastes old, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:31.89,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:33.07,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:38.22,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Queen of Witches, what did you do to Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:41.12,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's grimoire is giving off an eerie light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:44.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You almost look like... a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:47.79,main,vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 63: "It's Nothing."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.79,0:23:50.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 63\N\N{\fs18} It's Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:49.96,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,A black meteor shoots across the sky.
